PIXART IMAGING I said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 20.17% to NT$222,060,000 from NT$278,181,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            222,060          278,181    
YOY%             -20.17%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            839,400          956,153    
